            <title>[LU-9083] Add scripts to collect and analyze Lustre RPC traces</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9083</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A set of scripts to collect and analyze RPC traces in a Lustre file system. These scripts turn the Lustre debug-daemon on and off, before and after launching a job respectively. They also allow users to parse and visualize the logged RPC traces.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
